++ [[[Now, The Serpent]]] 

A tale series about the [[[serpent-s-hand-hub|Serpent's Hand]]] - about what they stand for, and what they stand against. A work in progress, but I hope that one day it will be complete.

My first published article, which hints at things to come:
[[[the-emperor-of-many-voices| The Emperor of Many Voices]]], coauthored by [[*user Dr Ore]] and [[*user slashannemoo]]

